trance sound. Liam Wilson - 'Summer Sun' is also featured as an amazing
full-length exclusive on this Sampler and the last spot belongs to Manuel
Rocca and his slammer 'No Turning Back'! Four smashing records for sampler
number four; what else could you possibly need?
